âœ… 3. Improve Progress Bar State

At start of generateHash():

progressBar.setValue(0);
progressBar.setString("Processing...");


---

âœ… 4. Add resetAll() Method (NEW)

private void resetAll() {
    selectedFile = null;
    fileField.setText("");
    resultArea.setText("");
    progressBar.setValue(0);
    progressBar.setString("Ready");
}

This resets the app to exactly how it was on startup.


